		<defName>AnAl_CreateChimera</defName>
		<label>chimera creation</label>
		<description>Induce a dark archotech to morph target animal(s) into a friendly chimera. The chimera can be trained to guard, attack, rescue, and haul. The total meat yield of the animal(s) must be at least equal to the meat yield of a chimera; any excess will be refunded as twisted meat. If the ritual isn't done properly, the animal(s) will morph into a hostile fleshbeast. The chance of this happening can be reduced by using more animals, along with the other ways of increasing ritual quality.</description>
